rows.label: fev05_320_125_msg0001
rows.name: Sorry to have kept you all waiting.

rows.label: fev05_320_125_msg0004
rows.name:
Hikari-chan did
most of the talking.

rows.label: fev05_320_125_msg0005
rows.name:
You two knew each other from before,
right?

rows.label: fev05_320_125_msg0009
rows.name:
You must be tired after today's events,
so please stay with us for another night.

rows.label: fev05_320_125_msg0010
rows.name:
Indeed... We only had an audience
with His Holiness Marveni,
but I feel thoroughly exhausted.

rows.label: fev05_320_125_msg0011
rows.name: Shall we accept their offer to rest?

rows.label: fev05_320_125_msg0012
rows.name:
Yeah, sounds good.
Let's accept their hospitality.

rows.label: fev05_320_125_msg0013
rows.name:
Tora very happy!
Get to sleep in fluffy bed
again tonight!

rows.label: fev05_320_125_msg0014
rows.name: Then shall we return to the cathedral?
